                    target="_blank">Most polar bears could struggle to survive in the Arctic by 2100</a></h3>
                <p>For many people, there is one animal that comes to mind when they think of creatures threatened by
                  climate change: the polar bear.In recent years, images of emaciated bears searching desperately for
                  food have made the Arctic's apex
                  predator the poster child for the effects of global warming.</p>
              </div>
